> Module Earnings

# Earnings exclusions (sub-module)

## Declarations

```catala-metadata
declaration structure EarningsResult:
  data excluded_amount content money
  data remaining_earned_income content money

declaration scope ApplyExclusions:
  input gross_earned_income content money
  output result content EarningsResult
```

## Earned-income exclusion

*Source: policy.md — Section 1. Earnings exclusions*

```catala
scope ApplyExclusions:
  definition result equals
    let excluded equals
      if gross_earned_income <= $65 then gross_earned_income
      else $65 + (gross_earned_income - $65) * 50%
    in
    EarningsResult {
      -- excluded_amount: excluded
      -- remaining_earned_income: gross_earned_income - excluded
    }
```
